### Bootstrap
    Topics include:

    What is Bootstrap?
    The grid system and Bootstrap layouts
    Bootstrap components
  #Advantages
    -Saves time
      With a host of pre-built components and designs, you can save loads of time by using the Bootstrap templates.
    -Mobile first
      Bootstrap 3 comes with a mobile-first approach, so you can easily create responsive designs.
    -Easy to use
      Bootstrap is easy to use. Now that you have knowledge of HTML and CSS, we can use all the functionality of Bootstrap.
    -Cross-browser compatibility
      Bootstrap is compatible with all modern browsers.
    -Its free
      It’s open source and completely free to download and modify as you wish.
  #The setup
    http://getbootstrap.com/getting-started/#download
  # Grid System
    -The rows can be laid out as one 1 column, split into 12 separate columns, or anything in between.
    -12 is the maximum number of columns permitted per row and they are also the units used to measure the width of the page horizontally.
      The sum of columns in a row must equal 12
    -Column layout examples
      Three-column layout
      <div class="col-sm-4">...</div>
      <div class="col-sm-4">...</div>
      <div class="col-sm-4">...</div>
    -How to implement
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row">
             <div class="col-sm-4">
                   ...
             </div>
             <div class="col-sm-4">
                   ...
             </div>
             <div class="col-sm-4">
                   ...
             </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
               ...
          </div>
        </div>
      -Column syntax
        class="col-sm-4"

        col – This element is a column
        sm – This is the screen size, in this example “small” (we will cover this in more detail in the next section).
        4 – The width of the column (out of 12)
        <div class="col-sm-4">...</div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">...</div>
        <div class="col-sm-4">...</div>
      -center a grid
      <div class="row">
           <div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-4">.col-md-4 .col-md-offset-4</div>
       </div>
  #Basic Components
    -bootstrap buttons
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-success">Learn</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-success">Learn</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Learn</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-danger">Learn</a>

      <a href="#" class="btn btn-success btn-lg">Learn</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary btn-default">Learn</a>
      <a href="#" class="btn btn-danger btn-sm">Learn</a>
    -Bootstrap lists
      <ul>
        <li>Chrome</li>
        <li>Firefox</li>
        <li>Safari</li>
        <li>Opera</li>
        <li>Internet Explorer
          <ul>
            <li>IE</li>
            <li>Edge</li>
          </ul>
        </li>
          <li>Torch</li>
      </ul>
      -Boostrap list groups
        <ul class="list-group">
          <li class="list-group-item">Stars</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">Songs</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">Photos</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">Comments</li>
        </ul>
      -Glyphs
        <div class="list-group">
          <li class="list-group-item">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span> Stars
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item active">
              <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-music"></span> Songs
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item">
              <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-camera"></span> Photos
          </li>
          <li class="list-group-item ">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-comment"></span> Comments
          </li>
        </div>
      -Badges
        <div class="list-group">
          <a href="#" class="list-group-item">
              <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star-empty"></span> Stars
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="list-group-item active">
              <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-music"></span> Songs
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="list-group-item">
              <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-camera"></span> Photos
          </a>
          <a href="#" class="list-group-item ">
              <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-comment"></span> Comments
          </a>
        </div>

        -Add span
          <a href="#" class="list-group-item">
             <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-star"></span> Stars
             <span class="badge">145</span>
          </a>

